This article is an executive order issued by President Barack Obama on June 17, 2015. The order states that amendments are being made to the Manual for Courts-Martial, United States, which is the military's legal system. The specific amendments are detailed in an attached annex. The order also clarifies that the amendments will not retroactively punish any acts committed before the effective date of the order. It also states that any ongoing nonjudicial punishment proceedings, investigations, trials, or other actions can continue unaffected by the amendments.